Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-rich, python3-psutil, python3-textual
Description: Network monitoring and system log dashboard
 A modular Linux terminal tool similar to htop, but focused on
 real-time network activity, user login monitoring, and log-based alerts.
 .
 Features:
  * Real-time network statistics per interface
  * Current and recent user login tracking
  * System log monitoring with alerts for security events
